-- HOW IT WORKS: identical to the FL seed (docs/florida-development-reports-seed.sql)
-- with _nj_zips and vintage 'zipcodes PyPI v3.0.0 centroid; get-address-report ZIP
-- mode; New Jersey batch 2026-07-17'. Runs on the fail-loud engine.
